the big, bad wolf."

10
00:02:20,259 --> 00:02:22,613
Did they really kill the wolf,
Mum?

11
00:02:22,637 --> 00:02:25,198
I'm sure they did.

12
00:02:25,222 --> 00:02:27,701
I'll kill the monster
when it comes.

13
00:02:27,725 --> 00:02:29,893
I'll smash its head in.

14
00:02:32,313 --> 00:02:34,291
It's time to go to sleep now,
sweetie.

15
00:02:34,315 --> 00:02:35,834
It's very late.

16
00:02:35,858 --> 00:02:38,777
Can we read it again?

17
00:02:41,906 --> 00:02:45,510
"A long time ago -
just yesterday, in fact -

18
00:02:45,534 --> 00:02:50,580
"there were three little pigs
and one nasty big wolf."

19
00:04:02,695 --> 00:04:03,839
What have you done?

20
00:04:03,863 --> 00:04:05,674
It's not broken.
It just slipped.

21
00:04:05,698 --> 00:04:08,051
I don't want you firing
things off in the house anymore.

22
00:04:08,075 --> 00:04:11,221
Wait, wait, wait. Watch this. When the
monster comes, I'm gonna do this.

23
00:04:11,245 --> 00:04:12,453
Please don't!

24
00:04:16,125 --> 00:04:17,477
Nothing in my hands.

25
00:04:17,501 --> 00:04:20,105
- Nothing in my hands.
- Stand still, please.

26
00:04:20,129 --> 00:04:21,690
Look at me, Mum!

27
00:04:21,714 --> 00:04:22,941
Come on, Samuel.

28
00:04:22,965 --> 00:04:25,277
- Look at me.
- Stand still, please.

29
00:04:25,301 --> 00:04:27,195
Nothing in my hands.
Nothing in my hands.

30
00:04:27,219 --> 00:04:28,780
I don't want you
making weapons anymore.

31
00:04:28,804 --> 00:04:30,782
It doesn't work
if you don't look at me.

32
00:04:30,806 --> 00:04:34,017
This monster thing
has got to stop, alright?

33
00:04:47,531 --> 00:04:49,782
Don't do that!

34
00:04:52,495 --> 00:04:53,953
Ready?

35
00:04:56,207 --> 00:04:57,832
Come on.

36
00:05:02,338 --> 00:05:03,940
Quick. You're late already.

37
00:05:03,964 --> 00:05:05,734
